TASK 1 — File and Directory Management  (15 pts, ~12 min)
Upravljanje datotekama i direktorijima
----------------------------------------------------------
You are organizing project files for the university IT department.
Organizirate projektne datoteke za IT odjel fakulteta.

1. Create the directory /home/student/projects/{{ exam_dir }} with all
   intermediate directories.  (2 pts)
   Stvorite direktorij /home/student/projects/{{ exam_dir }} sa svim
   međudirektorijima.

2. Inside that directory, create three empty files:
   report.txt, backup.txt, notes.txt.  (2 pts)
   Unutar tog direktorija stvorite tri prazne datoteke:
   report.txt, backup.txt, notes.txt.

3. Copy /etc/hostname to /home/student/projects/{{ exam_dir }}/hostname.txt.  (2 pts)
   Kopirajte /etc/hostname u /home/student/projects/{{ exam_dir }}/hostname.txt.

4. Append the last 5 lines of /etc/passwd to
   /home/student/projects/{{ exam_dir }}/report.txt.  (3 pts)
   Dodajte zadnjih 5 redaka datoteke /etc/passwd na kraj
   /home/student/projects/{{ exam_dir }}/report.txt.

5. Create a hard link to report.txt at the path:
   /home/student/projects/report-link-{{ exam_variant }}.  (3 pts)
