   containing exactly / koji sadrži točno:
   {{ exam_mount_text }}
   (2 pts)

4. Find all files in /etc larger than 50 KB and save the full path
   list to {{ exam_mount }}/large-files.txt.  (3 pts)
   Pronađite sve datoteke u /etc veće od 50 KB i spremite popis
